# DRAFT — bg-luminance-aware text composition curve for GPUI's mac monochrome
# text path (kitty text_composition_strategy "1.7 30" ≡ SwiftTerm .appleApprox).
#
# Target: zed-industries/zed @ 10b07951838e422722e34641f4a9c0bfec9037ff
# Status: drafted from source reading for SIZING (spike-1 deliverable 6).
#         NOT applied, NOT compiled. Hunk line numbers are approximate; apply
#         by context. See bg-luminance-patch-plan.md for the full analysis.
#
# Semantics: MonochromeSprite.bg_luminance < 0 (default everywhere except
# callers that opt in via TextRun.background_color) => curve disabled =>
# byte-identical output for all existing GPUI users (upstreamable as opt-in).

